msgstr "(Screencast) Starten Sie einen neuen Ticket-Dialog aus i-doit heraus"

#: ../extras/i-doit-track-company-property.rst:79
msgid ""
"Use the **📄 Create ticket** button in the asset ticket list to start a new, "
