#~ msgid ""
#~ "Tickets also have metadata attached to them to make them easier to "
#~ "manage. For instance, tickets have a customer and (optionally) an agent; "
#~ "they can be open or closed (or even be scheduled for later); they can be "
#~ "organized into groups; and they can even be flagged for high or low "
#~ "priority."
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "Tickets besitzen weiterhin noch Metadaten, um sie einfacher zu verwalten. "
